cs.GT, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.AI 

The paper proposes a new type of auction for keyword search advertising, which involves game theory (cs.GT) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. The paper also discusses the use of dynamic programming strategies, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the use of algorithms and data structures to optimize the auction process, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
